-children.#comment: TimeSensors for the rotor blades and anti-collision light
Interpolators for incrementing rotor blade rotation
The list of materials to be used throughout the model
cannot USE a node under StaticGroup, thus parent is Group
The main rotor group contains the routing nodes for animation of the main rotor blades
The tail rotor group contains the routing nodes for animation of the tail rotor blades
The gun group contains transforms for the turret and gun, suitable for inclusion of routing nodes for animation of the turret (not implemented in this model)

The wing weapons group contains all of the wingstub ordnance; this includes 8 Hellfire missiles and 14 High Explosive 2.75" rockets. This facilitates animations of individual elements such as a missile launch (not implemented in this model)
The lights group contains all the aircraft lights, to include the interpolators and routing nodes to animate cyclic lighting for the anti-collision light.
